  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, the increasing sophistication and accessibility of tools like ChatGPT raises concern about their potential use to commit acts of fraud in assessments [36].",
    "Therefore, special attention must be paid to implementing measures to prevent plagiarism and ensure the authenticity of the work presented.",
    "Proposed Activities to Develop Research Competencies Using ChatGPTStudents are encouraged to use ChatGPT as a tool to develop interactive research proposals.",
    "This process involves the formulation of hypotheses, defining clear objectives, and designing an appropriate methodology.",
    "By providing ChatGPT with a research topic and relevant context, the system assists students in generating hypotheses and refining their research framework."
  ]
}